attributes.title: Memory (A Discourse delivered at Inner Awakening & LBE)
attributes.description: This discourse was delivered by Living Enlightened Master Paramahamsa Nithyananda at the recently concluded Inner Awakening Program in Benguluru, India.  Inner Awakening is a 21 day enlightenement intensive program to establish one in Jivan Mukti or Living Enlightenment.  The next Inner Awakening program will be held at Benuguluru from December 2-22, 2009.  For more information please visit www.dhyanapeetam.org
